WEBVTT

00:05:29.820 --> 00:05:33.031
Are we knowingly causing
a mass extinction?

00:05:33.738 --> 00:05:35.429
Are we evil?

00:05:37.118 --> 00:05:39.299
No, of course not.

00:05:39.700 --> 00:05:41.329
People keep doing what they do

00:05:41.329 --> 00:05:43.969
because the vast majority
doesn't have a clue

00:05:43.969 --> 00:05:47.722
about the actual consequences
of our everyday life,

00:05:48.474 --> 00:05:51.449
and they don't know
that rapid change is required.

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:56.446
We all think we know,
and we all think everybody knows,

00:05:56.447 --> 00:05:58.020
but we don't.

00:05:58.708 --> 00:06:00.339
Because how could we?